  </div>
</section>

{%- elsif page.handle == 'shipping-returns' -%}

<div class="policy-page">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="policy-title">Shipping &amp; Returns</h1>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">Shipping</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">We offer free standard shipping on all orders to Canada and the United States. No minimum order required.</p>
      <div class="policy-table">
        <div class="policy-table-row policy-table-header">
          <span>Region</span>
          <span>Carrier</span>
          <span>Estimated Delivery</span>
        </div>
        <div class="policy-table-row">
          <span>Canada</span>
          <span>Canada Post</span>
          <span>5 to 8 business days</span>
        </div>
        <div class="policy-table-row">
          <span>United States</span>
          <span>USPS / Canada Post</span>
          <span>7 to 12 business days</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="policy-para">Orders are processed within 1 to 2 business days. You will receive a tracking number by email once your order ships.</p>
      <p class="policy-para">We do not currently ship outside of Canada and the United States. Email us at <a href="mailto:Lalumecare@gmail.com">Lalumecare@gmail.com</a> if you are located elsewhere.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">30-Day Money-Back Guarantee</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">If you are not visibly happier with your skin within 30 days of receiving your order, we will refund you in full. No receipt required. No product return required. No questions asked.</p>
      <p class="policy-para">To request a refund, email <a href="mailto:Lalumecare@gmail.com">Lalumecare@gmail.com</a> with your order number. Refunds are processed within 3 to 5 business days to the original payment method.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">Damaged or Incorrect Orders</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">If your order arrives damaged or you received the wrong item, contact us at <a href="mailto:Lalumecare@gmail.com">Lalumecare@gmail.com</a> within 7 days of delivery with your order number and a photo. We will send a replacement at no cost.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">Questions</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">Email us at <a href="mailto:Lalumecare@gmail.com">Lalumecare@gmail.com</a>. We reply within 24 hours on business days.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{%- elsif page.handle == 'privacy-policy' -%}

<div class="policy-page">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="policy-title">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">Who We Are</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">LaLume Skincare is a Canadian skincare brand based in British Columbia. We are responsible for the personal information you share with us when you place an order or subscribe to our emails. Questions about this policy: <a href="mailto:Lalumecare@gmail.com">Lalumecare@gmail.com</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">When you place an order, we collect your name, shipping address, email address, phone number, and payment information. Payment details are processed securely by Shopify Payments and are never stored on our servers.</p>
      <p class="policy-para">When you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect your email address only. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link at the bottom of any email we send.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">We use your information to fulfill your order, send shipping updates, and respond to customer service inquiries. If you have opted in, we may also send product updates and skincare content by email.</p>
      <p class="policy-para">We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for their own marketing purposes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">Under Canadian privacy law (PIPEDA), you have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of the personal information we hold about you. To exercise any of these rights, email <a href="mailto:Lalumecare@gmail.com">Lalumecare@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">Cookies</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">Our website uses cookies to keep items in your cart, remember your preferences, and measure site traffic. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though some features may not function correctly.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{%- elsif page.handle == 'contact' -%}

<div class="policy-page">
